Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.60,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:20.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.51,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.19,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.37,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:22.67,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:27.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:34.43,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago we had a brief encounter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody else remembers it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on the other side of the hedge with a red shovel in your dirt-covered hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke with brightly beaming eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye! See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a rainy day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago. A brief encounter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If someday, somehow, I discover that you remember that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, I intend to confess to you that I also remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you are going in that dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even thought the school does have a uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the rules do say that it is ok to wear regular clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...at least, as long as the clothes are suitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. Who in the world would wear ordinary clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to attend their high school orientation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Check with your father before you act foollish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you always say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, that looks really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you look like a genuine high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very cute. It's splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, You're always exaggerating...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother, my dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today I started high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course I am not so naive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as to think it will change my life completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, this year's cherry blossoms will be just the same as last year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... But still, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel so excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you hear my heart racing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,1. The Magnificent Ones
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We barely made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so good in the uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were not going to wear a uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going to wear your favorite dress, you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is someone in my family who is hard-headed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She is not a {\i1}Kiyouiku{\i0} Mama, but she's still very conservative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here. She said, "It is common sense to wear a uniform for your orientation."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly what MY mom said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad... We choose Seiran school because they allow regular clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cute!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...and "Splendid"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy's little darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother, to tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My father is not my father by birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I was five, my mother remarried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:13.50,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,We are proceeding to City Hall by way of Seiran School.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.18,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Next stop is Gouen-mae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But now... I love my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He is kind, and intelligent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a beautiful bracelet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.58,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,This stop is Seiran School.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm getting off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not used to this bus yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here... you dropped this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here... you dropped this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she spoke her voice was clear like a bell,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet also deep and soothing, like a gentle breeze blowing through my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is wearing a uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, I'm in section A...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in... um... section B.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been in the same section since grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A little, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.40,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Please assemble in the Auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.44,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,The orientation is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be seeing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the students in uniform are from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the students from the Fuzoku schools would be wearing a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Being from the outside, though, you must really be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll show my secret to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have red nail polish on my thumb nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So red! So beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are cute and likeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You are... I hope... in section B?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Shinobu Mariko. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,An unusual name...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be using that herbal shampoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I love that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Or we'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru no Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kaoru no Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kaoru no Kimi! Look! that's Kaoru no Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't leave after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Udaishow Kaoru no Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru no Kimi-sama! How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We were worried that you might leave our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From today on, I will just be a freshman like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you intend to continue the club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Her real name is Orihara Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She is in our section, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let' sit down! The orientation is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a year older than us, but she was away for a long time due to illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, go on and sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}perhaps this year's cherry blossoms
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will end up being very different from last year's after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:14.06,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,The class president will now speak to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may not believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but her lips are wet and shining like wild berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She is Ichinomiya Fukiko. We call her "Miya-sama". She is our queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The ladies behind her are the Sorority members.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama? Sorority members?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want so much to become a Sorority member.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That has been my dream since I came to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am confident I will be selected as a candidate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a social group popular in the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,New members are chosen by established members of the Sorority
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,based on their looks, grades, family and health.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,During your freshman year, all of you become eligible
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to become candidates for entry into the Seiran Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you become a member,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you are invited to parties, meetings, seminars, finishing lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you are introduced to nice boyfriends too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a ticket to a wonderful life here at our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, those who have even the least confidence in their looks or grades...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...are desperately seeking to be noticed by the Sorority sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon our members will select a few candidates who meet our standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We will invite the candidates to a party to finalize selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This year the number of candidates will be limited to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten? Only Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Saint-Juste! Hana no Saint-Juste!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama! Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana no Saint-Juste-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There are three beautiful ladies here that everybody adores.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru no Kimi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya Fukiko-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hana no Saint-Juste-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the Music hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get to know her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants this lucky red rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw her, I saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Hana no Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The lady I saw in the bus today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She plays piano so beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kaoru no Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She is in my section.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks very healthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone back from a long sick leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up. It's going to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A Spring storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossoms will end soon, won't they...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably with this rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain comes every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It always rains on the days important to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I like things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't rain that other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority will only take ten new members!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all our class talks about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole school seems to be excited about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Our class is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In our class we have daughters of company presidents,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,daughters of ambassadors, and of politicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and daughters of professors of prestigious colleges!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's you, the daughter of a professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My father would laugh until he burst...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't really travel in such circles, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, let's start thinking about what dresses to wear to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We should! You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But Misaki-san surely you would be the best possible candidate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is a famous lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and in every criteria you are superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it depends on how they will judge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She is also in section B.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama! Hana no Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she called Saint-Juste? What's her real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose outsiders like you wouldn't know much at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She is Asaka Rei from the sophomore class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Asaka Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama is going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can ever fit in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the one I met in the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For goodness sake, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Are you day dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The bus won't come for another fifteen minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't have umbrellas to walk to the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Another letter from that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why'd you want to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a break from working on my thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. Sure, fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we go, I need to go shopping for a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to buy a Nyugaku-iwai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance into high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Small world, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Her going to Seiran...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sending that with your name on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You really want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the professor and his wife will find out who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is how my first day at high school ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surrounded by some beautiful upperclasswomen and a rather worldly classmate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is with a sense of wonder and bewilderment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that I now see my Junior High years fading forever into the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a wonderful day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Spring Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... couldn't imagine anything more fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:13.91,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:19.42,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.88,0:24:25.09,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.09,0:24:30.55,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.22,0:24:36.77,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:42.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.21,0:24:45.01,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.01,0:24:47.81,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.81,0:24:50.16,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.16,0:24:55.37,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.09,0:25:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Sorority selection day approaches and all the girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.02,0:25:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,including Shinobu Mariko and Misaki Aya, are getting more and more nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.22,0:25:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day of selection,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.23,0:25:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the names Miya-sama spoke surprise everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.90,0:25:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How will Nanako and Misaki-san react?...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Glass Slippers
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.50,0:25:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
